title: Citizen Eco-Drive Rose Gold Mens Watch AO9023-01A Overview
description:

A modern classic rediscovered with this analog day/date dress timepiece. In stainless steel gold tone with a silver dial brown leather strap and day-date feature.

• Movement: Eco-Drive 8635
• Functions: 3 Hand Day-Date
• Band: Brown Leather Strap Buckle
• Case Size: 43mm
• Case Material: Rose Gold Tone Stainless Steel
• Crystal: Mineral Crystal
• Water Resistance: WR100 - 333ft (100m)
